                             21:package org.apache.poi.hslf.record;                                                                                                                                              
                             22:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             23:import static org.apache.logging.log4j.util.Unbox.box;                                                                                                                           
                             24:import static org.apache.poi.hslf.record.RecordAtom.getMaxRecordLength;                                                                                                          
                             25:import static org.apache.poi.hslf.usermodel.HSLFSlideShow.PP95_DOCUMENT;                                                                                                         
                             26:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             27:import java.io.IOException;                                                                                                                                                      
                             28:import java.io.InputStream;                                                                                                                                                      
                             29:import java.io.OutputStream;                                                                                                                                                     
                             30:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             31:import org.apache.commons.io.output.UnsynchronizedByteArrayOutputStream;                                                                                                         
                             32:import org.apache.logging.log4j.Logger;                                                                                                                                          
                             33:import org.apache.poi.logging.PoiLogManager;                                                                                                                                     
                             34:import org.apache.poi.hslf.exceptions.CorruptPowerPointFileException;                                                                                                            
                             35:import org.apache.poi.hslf.exceptions.OldPowerPointFormatException;                                                                                                              
                             36:import org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem.DirectoryNode;                                                                                                                            
                             37:import org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem.DocumentEntry;                                                                                                                            
                             38:import org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem.Entry;                                                                                                                                    
                             39:import org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem.POIFSFileSystem;                                                                                                                          
                             40:import org.apache.poi.util.IOUtils;                                                                                                                                              
                             41:import org.apache.poi.util.LittleEndian;                                                                                                                                         
                             42:import org.apache.poi.util.StringUtil;                                                                                                                                           
                             43:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             44:/**                                                                                                                                                                              
                             45: * This is a special kind of Atom, because it doesn't live inside the                                                                                                            
                             46: *  PowerPoint document. Instead, it lives in a separate stream in the                                                                                                           
                             47: *  document. As such, it has to be treated specially                                                                                                                            
                             48: */                                                                                                                                                                              
                             49:public class CurrentUserAtom {                                                                                                                                                   
                             50:    private static final Logger LOG = PoiLogManager.getLogger(CurrentUserAtom.class);                                                                                            
                             51:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             52:    /** Standard Atom header */                                                                                                                                                  
                             53:    private static final byte[] atomHeader = new byte[] { 0, 0, -10, 15 };                                                                                                       
                             54:    /** The PowerPoint magic number for a non-encrypted file */                                                                                                                  
                             55:    private static final byte[] headerToken = new byte[] { 95, -64, -111, -29 };                                                                                                 
                             56:    /** The PowerPoint magic number for an encrypted file */                                                                                                                     
                             57:    private static final byte[] encHeaderToken = new byte[] { -33, -60, -47, -13 };                                                                                              
                             58:    // The Powerpoint 97 version, major and minor numbers                                                                                                                        
                             59:    // byte[] ppt97FileVer = new byte[] { 8, 00, -13, 03, 03, 00 };                                                                                                              
                             60:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             61:    /** The version, major and minor numbers */                                                                                                                                  
                             62:    private int docFinalVersion;                                                                                                                                                 
                             63:    private byte docMajorNo;                                                                                                                                                     
                             64:    private byte docMinorNo;                                                                                                                                                     
                             65:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             66:    /** The Offset into the file for the current edit */                                                                                                                         
                             67:    private long currentEditOffset;                                                                                                                                              
                             68:    /** The Username of the last person to edit the file */                                                                                                                      
                             69:    private String lastEditUser;                                                                                                                                                 
                             70:    /** The document release version. Almost always 8 */                                                                                                                         
                             71:    private long releaseVersion;                                                                                                                                                 
                             72:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             73:    /** Only correct after reading in or writing out */                                                                                                                          
                             74:    private byte[] _contents;                                                                                                                                                    
                             75:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             76:    /** Flag for encryption state of the whole file */                                                                                                                           
                             77:    private boolean isEncrypted;                                                                                                                                                 
                             78:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             79:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             80:    /* ********************* getter/setter follows *********************** */                                                                                                    
                             81:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             82:    public int  getDocFinalVersion() { return docFinalVersion; }                                                                                                                 
                             83:    public byte getDocMajorNo()       { return docMajorNo; }                                                                                                                     
                             84:    public byte getDocMinorNo()       { return docMinorNo; }                                                                                                                     
                             85:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             86:    public long getReleaseVersion()  { return releaseVersion; }                                                                                                                  
                             87:    public void setReleaseVersion(long rv) { releaseVersion = rv; }                                                                                                              
                             88:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             89:    /** Points to the UserEditAtom */                                                                                                                                            
                             90:    public long getCurrentEditOffset() { return currentEditOffset; }                                                                                                             
                             91:    public void setCurrentEditOffset(long id ) { currentEditOffset = id; }                                                                                                       
                             92:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             93:    public String getLastEditUsername() { return lastEditUser; }                                                                                                                 
                             94:    public void setLastEditUsername(String u) { lastEditUser = u; }                                                                                                              
                             95:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             96:    public boolean isEncrypted() { return isEncrypted; }                                                                                                                         
                             97:    public void setEncrypted(boolean isEncrypted) { this.isEncrypted = isEncrypted; }                                                                                            
                             98:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             99:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             100:    /* ********************* real code follows *************************** */                                                                                                   
                             101:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             102:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             103:     * Create a new Current User Atom                                                                                                                                           
                             104:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             105:    public CurrentUserAtom() {                                                                                                                                                  
                             106:        _contents = new byte[0];                                                                                                                                                
                             107:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             108:        // Initialise to empty                                                                                                                                                  
                             109:        docFinalVersion = 0x03f4;                                                                                                                                               
                             110:        docMajorNo = 3;                                                                                                                                                         
                             111:        docMinorNo = 0;                                                                                                                                                         
                             112:        releaseVersion = 8;                                                                                                                                                     
                             113:        currentEditOffset = 0;                                                                                                                                                  
                             114:        lastEditUser = "Apache POI";                                                                                                                                            
                             115:        isEncrypted = false;                                                                                                                                                    
                             116:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             117:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             118:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             119:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             120:     * Find the Current User in the filesystem, and create from that                                                                                                            
                             121:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             122:    public CurrentUserAtom(DirectoryNode dir) throws IOException {                                                                                                              
                             123:        // Decide how big it is                                                                                                                                                 
                             124:        final Entry entry = dir.getEntry("Current User");                                                                                                                       
                             125:        if (!(entry instanceof DocumentEntry)) {                                                                                                                                
                             126:            throw new IllegalArgumentException("Had unexpected type of entry for name: Current User: " + entry.getClass());                                                     
                             127:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             128:        DocumentEntry docProps = (DocumentEntry) entry;                                                                                                                         
                             129:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             130:        // If it's clearly junk, bail out                                                                                                                                       
                             131:        if(docProps.getSize() > 131072) {                                                                                                                                       
                             132:            throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("The Current User stream is implausibly long. It's normally 28-200 bytes long, but was " +                                 
                             docProps.getSize() + " bytes");                                                                                                                                                     
                             133:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             134:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             135:        // Grab the contents                                                                                                                                                    
                             136:        try (InputStream in = dir.createDocumentInputStream("Current User")) {                                                                                                  
                             137:            _contents = IOUtils.toByteArray(in, docProps.getSize(), getMaxRecordLength());                                                                                      
                             138:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             139:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             140:        // See how long it is. If it's under 28 bytes long, we can't                                                                                                            
                             141:        //  read it                                                                                                                                                             
                             142:        if(_contents.length < 28) {                                                                                                                                             
                             143:            boolean isPP95 = dir.hasEntryCaseInsensitive(PP95_DOCUMENT);                                                                                                        
                             144:            // PPT95 has 4 byte size, then data                                                                                                                                 
                             145:            if (!isPP95 && _contents.length >= 4) {                                                                                                                             
                             146:                int size = LittleEndian.getInt(_contents);                                                                                                                      
                             147:                isPP95 = (size + 4 == _contents.length);                                                                                                                        
                             148:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             149:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             150:            if (isPP95) {                                                                                                                                                       
                             151:                throw new OldPowerPointFormatException("Based on the Current User stream, you seem to have supplied a PowerPoint95 file, which isn't                            
                             supported");                                                                                                                                                                        
                             152:            } else {                                                                                                                                                            
                             153:                throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("The Current User stream must be at least 28 bytes long, but was only " + _contents.length);                           
                             154:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             155:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             156:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             157:        // Set everything up                                                                                                                                                    
                             158:        init();                                                                                                                                                                 
                             159:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             160:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             161:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             162:     * Actually do the creation from a block of bytes                                                                                                                           
                             163:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             164:    private void init() {                                                                                                                                                       
                             165:        // First up is the size, in 4 bytes, which is fixed                                                                                                                     
                             166:        // Then is the header                                                                                                                                                   
                             167:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             168:        isEncrypted = (LittleEndian.getInt(encHeaderToken) == LittleEndian.getInt(_contents,12));                                                                               
                             169:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             170:        // Grab the edit offset                                                                                                                                                 
                             171:        currentEditOffset = LittleEndian.getUInt(_contents,16);                                                                                                                 
                             172:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             173:        // Grab the versions                                                                                                                                                    
                             174:        docFinalVersion = LittleEndian.getUShort(_contents,22);                                                                                                                 
                             175:        docMajorNo = _contents[24];                                                                                                                                             
                             176:        docMinorNo = _contents[25];                                                                                                                                             
                             177:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             178:        // Get the username length                                                                                                                                              
                             179:        long usernameLen = LittleEndian.getUShort(_contents,20);                                                                                                                
                             180:        if(usernameLen > 512) {                                                                                                                                                 
                             181:            // Handle the case of it being garbage                                                                                                                              
                             182:            LOG.atWarn().log("Invalid username length {} found, treating as if there was no username set", box(usernameLen));                                                   
                             183:            usernameLen = 0;                                                                                                                                                    
                             184:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             185:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             186:        // Now we know the length of the username,                                                                                                                              
                             187:        //  use this to grab the revision                                                                                                                                       
                             188:        if(_contents.length >= 28+(int)usernameLen + 4) {                                                                                                                       
                             189:            releaseVersion = LittleEndian.getUInt(_contents,28+(int)usernameLen);                                                                                               
                             190:        } else {                                                                                                                                                                
                             191:            // No revision given, as not enough data. Odd                                                                                                                       
                             192:            releaseVersion = 0;                                                                                                                                                 
                             193:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             194:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             195:        // Grab the unicode username, if stored                                                                                                                                 
                             196:        int start = 28+(int)usernameLen+4;                                                                                                                                      
                             197:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             198:        if(_contents.length >= start+2*usernameLen) {                                                                                                                           
                             199:            lastEditUser = StringUtil.getFromUnicodeLE(_contents, start, (int)usernameLen);                                                                                     
                             200:        } else {                                                                                                                                                                
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             poi-scratchpad/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/hslf/usermodel/HSLFSlideShowImpl.java:315-364                                                                                           
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             315:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             316:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             317:    private void initRecordOffsets(byte[] docstream, int usrOffset, NavigableMap<Integer, Record> recordMap, Map<Integer, Integer> offset2id) {                                 
                             318:        while (usrOffset != 0) {                                                                                                                                                
                             319:            Record builtRecord = Record.buildRecordAtOffset(docstream, usrOffset);                                                                                              
                             320:            if (!(builtRecord instanceof UserEditAtom)) {                                                                                                                       
                             321:                throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("Did not have a user edit atom: " + builtRecord);                                                                      
                             322:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             323:            UserEditAtom usr = (UserEditAtom) builtRecord;                                                                                                                      
                             324:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             325:            recordMap.put(usrOffset, usr);                                                                                                                                      
                             326:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             327:            int psrOffset = usr.getPersistPointersOffset();                                                                                                                     
                             328:            Record record = Record.buildRecordAtOffset(docstream, psrOffset);                                                                                                   
                             329:            if (record == null) {                                                                                                                                               
                             330:                throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("Powerpoint document is missing a PersistPtrHolder at " + psrOffset);                                                  
                             331:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             332:            if (!(record instanceof PersistPtrHolder)) {                                                                                                                        
                             333:                throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("Record is not a PersistPtrHolder: " + record + " at " + psrOffset);                                                   
                             334:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             335:            PersistPtrHolder ptr = (PersistPtrHolder) record;                                                                                                                   
                             336:            recordMap.put(psrOffset, ptr);                                                                                                                                      
                             337:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             338:            for (Map.Entry<Integer, Integer> entry : ptr.getSlideLocationsLookup().entrySet()) {                                                                                
                             339:                Integer offset = entry.getValue();                                                                                                                              
                             340:                Integer id = entry.getKey();                                                                                                                                    
                             341:                recordMap.put(offset, null); // reserve a slot for the record                                                                                                   
                             342:                offset2id.put(offset, id);                                                                                                                                      
                             343:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             344:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             345:            usrOffset = usr.getLastUserEditAtomOffset();                                                                                                                        
                             346:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             347:            // check for corrupted user edit atom and try to repair it                                                                                                          
                             348:            // if the next user edit atom offset is already known, we would go into an endless loop                                                                             
                             349:            if (usrOffset > 0 && recordMap.containsKey(usrOffset)) {                                                                                                            
                             350:                // a user edit atom is usually located 36 byte before the smallest known record offset                                                                          
                             351:                usrOffset = recordMap.firstKey() - 36;                                                                                                                          
                             352:                // check that we really are located on a user edit atom                                                                                                         
                             353:                int ver_inst = LittleEndian.getUShort(docstream, usrOffset);                                                                                                    
                             354:                int type = LittleEndian.getUShort(docstream, usrOffset + 2);                                                                                                    
                             355:                int len = LittleEndian.getInt(docstream, usrOffset + 4);                                                                                                        
                             356:                if (ver_inst == 0 && type == 4085 && (len == 0x1C || len == 0x20)) {                                                                                            
                             357:                    LOG.atWarn().log("Repairing invalid user edit atom");                                                                                                       
                             358:                    usr.setLastUserEditAtomOffset(usrOffset);                                                                                                                   
                             359:                } else {                                                                                                                                                        
                             360:                    throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("Powerpoint document contains invalid user edit atom");                                                            
                             361:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             362:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             363:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             364:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             poi-scratchpad/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/hslf/usermodel/HSLFSlideShowImpl.java:315-364                                                                                           
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             315:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             316:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             317:    private void initRecordOffsets(byte[] docstream, int usrOffset, NavigableMap<Integer, Record> recordMap, Map<Integer, Integer> offset2id) {                                 
                             318:        while (usrOffset != 0) {                                                                                                                                                
                             319:            Record builtRecord = Record.buildRecordAtOffset(docstream, usrOffset);                                                                                              
                             320:            if (!(builtRecord instanceof UserEditAtom)) {                                                                                                                       
                             321:                throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("Did not have a user edit atom: " + builtRecord);                                                                      
                             322:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             323:            UserEditAtom usr = (UserEditAtom) builtRecord;                                                                                                                      
                             324:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             325:            recordMap.put(usrOffset, usr);                                                                                                                                      
                             326:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             327:            int psrOffset = usr.getPersistPointersOffset();                                                                                                                     
                             328:            Record record = Record.buildRecordAtOffset(docstream, psrOffset);                                                                                                   
                             329:            if (record == null) {                                                                                                                                               
                             330:                throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("Powerpoint document is missing a PersistPtrHolder at " + psrOffset);                                                  
                             331:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             332:            if (!(record instanceof PersistPtrHolder)) {                                                                                                                        
                             333:                throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("Record is not a PersistPtrHolder: " + record + " at " + psrOffset);                                                   
                             334:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             335:            PersistPtrHolder ptr = (PersistPtrHolder) record;                                                                                                                   
                             336:            recordMap.put(psrOffset, ptr);                                                                                                                                      
                             337:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             338:            for (Map.Entry<Integer, Integer> entry : ptr.getSlideLocationsLookup().entrySet()) {                                                                                
                             339:                Integer offset = entry.getValue();                                                                                                                              
                             340:                Integer id = entry.getKey();                                                                                                                                    
                             341:                recordMap.put(offset, null); // reserve a slot for the record                                                                                                   
                             342:                offset2id.put(offset, id);                                                                                                                                      
                             343:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             344:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             345:            usrOffset = usr.getLastUserEditAtomOffset();                                                                                                                        
                             346:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             347:            // check for corrupted user edit atom and try to repair it                                                                                                          
                             348:            // if the next user edit atom offset is already known, we would go into an endless loop                                                                             
                             349:            if (usrOffset > 0 && recordMap.containsKey(usrOffset)) {                                                                                                            
                             350:                // a user edit atom is usually located 36 byte before the smallest known record offset                                                                          
                             351:                usrOffset = recordMap.firstKey() - 36;                                                                                                                          
                             352:                // check that we really are located on a user edit atom                                                                                                         
                             353:                int ver_inst = LittleEndian.getUShort(docstream, usrOffset);                                                                                                    
                             354:                int type = LittleEndian.getUShort(docstream, usrOffset + 2);                                                                                                    
                             355:                int len = LittleEndian.getInt(docstream, usrOffset + 4);                                                                                                        
                             356:                if (ver_inst == 0 && type == 4085 && (len == 0x1C || len == 0x20)) {                                                                                            
                             357:                    LOG.atWarn().log("Repairing invalid user edit atom");                                                                                                       
                             358:                    usr.setLastUserEditAtomOffset(usrOffset);                                                                                                                   
                             359:                } else {                                                                                                                                                        
                             360:                    throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("Powerpoint document contains invalid user edit atom");                                                            
                             361:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             362:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             363:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             364:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>

                             -                if (ver_inst == 0 && type == 4085 && (len == 0x1C || len == 0x20)) {                                                                                               
                             -                    LOG.atWarn().log("Repairing invalid user edit atom");                                                                                                          
                             -                    usr.setLastUserEditAtomOffset(usrOffset);                                                                                                                      
                             -                } else {                                                                                                                                                           
                             -                    throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("Powerpoint document contains invalid user edit atom");                                                               
                             -                }                                                                                                                                                                  
                             -            }                                                                                                                                                                      
                             +            // validate usrOffset bounds to prevent infinite loops or buffer overrun                                                                                               
                             +            if (usrOffset < 0 || usrOffset + 8 > docstream.length) {                                                                                                               
                             +                throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("Invalid user edit atom offset out of bounds: " + usrOffset);                                                             
                             +            }                                                                                                                                                                      
                             +                                                                                                                                                                                   
                             +            // removed repair logic, cycle and bounds checks handle invalid offsets
