                             14:   See the License for the specific language governing permissions and                                                                                                           
                             15:   limitations under the License.                                                                                                                                                
                             16:==================================================================== */                                                                                                          
                             17:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             18:package org.apache.poi.hslf.record;                                                                                                                                              
                             19:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             20:import java.io.IOException;                                                                                                                                                      
                             21:import java.io.OutputStream;                                                                                                                                                     
                             22:import java.util.Arrays;                                                                                                                                                         
                             23:import java.util.Collections;                                                                                                                                                    
                             24:import java.util.LinkedHashMap;                                                                                                                                                  
                             25:import java.util.Map;                                                                                                                                                            
                             26:import java.util.function.Supplier;                                                                                                                                              
                             27:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             28:import org.apache.poi.hslf.exceptions.HSLFException;                                                                                                                             
                             29:import org.apache.poi.util.LittleEndian;                                                                                                                                         
                             30:import org.apache.poi.util.LittleEndianConsts;                                                                                                                                   
                             31:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             32:/**                                                                                                                                                                              
                             33: * A UserEdit Atom (type 4085). Holds information which bits of the file                                                                                                         
                             34: *  were last used by powerpoint, the version of powerpoint last used etc.                                                                                                       
                             35: *                                                                                                                                                                               
                             36: * ** WARNING ** stores byte offsets from the start of the PPT stream to                                                                                                         
                             37: *  other records! If you change the size of any elements before one of                                                                                                          
                             38: *  these, you'll need to update the offsets!                                                                                                                                    
                             39: */                                                                                                                                                                              
                             40:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             41:public final class UserEditAtom extends PositionDependentRecordAtom                                                                                                              
                             42:{                                                                                                                                                                                
                             43:    public static final int LAST_VIEW_NONE = 0;                                                                                                                                  
                             44:    public static final int LAST_VIEW_SLIDE_VIEW = 1;                                                                                                                            
                             45:    public static final int LAST_VIEW_OUTLINE_VIEW = 2;                                                                                                                          
                             46:    public static final int LAST_VIEW_NOTES = 3;                                                                                                                                 
                             47:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             48:    private byte[] _header;                                                                                                                                                      
                             49:    private static final long _type = RecordTypes.UserEditAtom.typeID;                                                                                                           
                             50:    private short unused;                                                                                                                                                        
                             51:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             52:    private int lastViewedSlideID;                                                                                                                                               
                             53:    private int pptVersion;                                                                                                                                                      
                             54:    private int lastUserEditAtomOffset;                                                                                                                                          
                             55:    private int persistPointersOffset;                                                                                                                                           
                             56:    private int docPersistRef;                                                                                                                                                   
                             57:    private int maxPersistWritten;                                                                                                                                               
                             58:    private short lastViewType;                                                                                                                                                  
                             59:    private int encryptSessionPersistIdRef = -1;                                                                                                                                 
                             60:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             61:    // Somewhat user facing getters                                                                                                                                              
                             62:    public int getLastViewedSlideID() { return lastViewedSlideID; }                                                                                                              
                             63:    public short getLastViewType()    { return lastViewType; }                                                                                                                   
                             64:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             65:    // Scary internal getters                                                                                                                                                    
                             66:    public int getLastUserEditAtomOffset() { return lastUserEditAtomOffset; }                                                                                                    
                             67:    public int getPersistPointersOffset()  { return persistPointersOffset; }                                                                                                     
                             68:    public int getDocPersistRef()          { return docPersistRef; }                                                                                                             
                             69:    public int getMaxPersistWritten()      { return maxPersistWritten; }                                                                                                         
                             70:    public int getEncryptSessionPersistIdRef() { return encryptSessionPersistIdRef; }                                                                                            
                             71:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             72:    // More scary internal setters                                                                                                                                               
                             73:    public void setLastUserEditAtomOffset(int offset) { lastUserEditAtomOffset = offset; }                                                                                       
                             74:    public void setPersistPointersOffset(int offset)  { persistPointersOffset = offset; }                                                                                        
                             75:    public void setLastViewType(short type)           { lastViewType=type; }                                                                                                     
                             76:    public void setMaxPersistWritten(int max)         { maxPersistWritten=max; }                                                                                                 
                             77:    public void setEncryptSessionPersistIdRef(int id) {                                                                                                                          
                             78:        encryptSessionPersistIdRef=id;                                                                                                                                           
                             79:        LittleEndian.putInt(_header,4,(id == -1 ? 28 : 32));                                                                                                                     
                             80:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             81:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             82:    /* *************** record code follows ********************** */                                                                                                             
                             83:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             84:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             85:     * For the UserEdit Atom                                                                                                                                                     
                             86:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             87:    protected UserEditAtom(byte[] source, int start, int len) {                                                                                                                  
                             88:        // Sanity Checking                                                                                                                                                       
                             89:        if(len < 34) { len = 34; }                                                                                                                                               
                             90:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             91:        int offset = start;                                                                                                                                                      
                             92:        // Get the header                                                                                                                                                        
                             93:        _header = Arrays.copyOfRange(source, start, start+8);                                                                                                                    
                             94:        offset += 8;                                                                                                                                                             
                             95:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             96:        // Get the last viewed slide ID                                                                                                                                          
                             97:        lastViewedSlideID = LittleEndian.getInt(source,offset);                                                                                                                  
                             98:        offset += LittleEndianConsts.INT_SIZE;                                                                                                                                   
                             99:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             100:        // Get the PPT version                                                                                                                                                  
                             101:        pptVersion = LittleEndian.getInt(source,offset);                                                                                                                        
                             102:        offset += LittleEndianConsts.INT_SIZE;                                                                                                                                  
                             103:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             104:        // Get the offset to the previous incremental save's UserEditAtom                                                                                                       
                             105:        // This will be the byte offset on disk where the previous one                                                                                                          
                             106:        //  starts, or 0 if this is the first one                                                                                                                               
                             107:        lastUserEditAtomOffset = LittleEndian.getInt(source,offset);                                                                                                            
                             108:        offset += LittleEndianConsts.INT_SIZE;                                                                                                                                  
                             109:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             110:        // Get the offset to the persist pointers                                                                                                                               
                             111:        // This will be the byte offset on disk where the preceding                                                                                                             
                             112:        //  PersistPtrFullBlock or PersistPtrIncrementalBlock starts                                                                                                            
                             113:        persistPointersOffset = LittleEndian.getInt(source,offset);                                                                                                             
                             114:        offset += LittleEndianConsts.INT_SIZE;                                                                                                                                  
                             115:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             116:        // Get the persist reference for the document persist object                                                                                                            
                             117:        // Normally seems to be 1                                                                                                                                               
                             118:        docPersistRef = LittleEndian.getInt(source,offset);                                                                                                                     
                             119:        offset += LittleEndianConsts.INT_SIZE;                                                                                                                                  
                             120:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             121:        // Maximum number of persist objects written                                                                                                                            
                             122:        maxPersistWritten = LittleEndian.getInt(source,offset);                                                                                                                 
                             123:        offset += LittleEndianConsts.INT_SIZE;                                                                                                                                  
                             124:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             125:        // Last view type                                                                                                                                                       
                             126:        lastViewType = LittleEndian.getShort(source,offset);                                                                                                                    
                             127:        offset += LittleEndianConsts.SHORT_SIZE;                                                                                                                                
                             128:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             129:        // unused                                                                                                                                                               
                             130:        unused = LittleEndian.getShort(source,offset);                                                                                                                          
                             131:        offset += LittleEndianConsts.SHORT_SIZE;                                                                                                                                
                             132:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             133:        // There might be a few more bytes, which are a reserved field                                                                                                          
                             134:        if (offset-start<len) {                                                                                                                                                 
                             135:            encryptSessionPersistIdRef = LittleEndian.getInt(source,offset);                                                                                                    
                             136:            offset += LittleEndianConsts.INT_SIZE;                                                                                                                              
                             137:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             138:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             139:        if(offset-start != len) {                                                                                                                                               
                             140:            throw new HSLFException("Having invalid data in UserEditAtom: "                                                                                                     
                             141:                    + "len: " + len + ", offset: " + offset + ", start: " + start);                                                                                             
                             142:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             143:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             144:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             145:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             146:     * We are of type 4085                                                                                                                                                      
                             147:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             148:    @Override                                                                                                                                                                   
                             149:    public long getRecordType() { return _type; }                                                                                                                               
                             150:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             151:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             152:     * At write-out time, update the references to PersistPtrs and                                                                                                              
                             153:     *  other UserEditAtoms to point to their new positions                                                                                                                     
                             154:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             155:    @Override                                                                                                                                                                   
                             156:    public void updateOtherRecordReferences(Map<Integer,Integer> oldToNewReferencesLookup) {                                                                                    
                             157:        // Look up the new positions of our preceding UserEditAtomOffset                                                                                                        
                             158:        if(lastUserEditAtomOffset != 0) {                                                                                                                                       
                             159:            Integer newLocation = oldToNewReferencesLookup.get(Integer.valueOf(lastUserEditAtomOffset));                                                                        
                             160:            if(newLocation == null) {                                                                                                                                           
                             161:                throw new HSLFException("Couldn't find the new location of the UserEditAtom that used to be at " + lastUserEditAtomOffset);                                     
                             162:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             163:            lastUserEditAtomOffset = newLocation.intValue();                                                                                                                    
                             164:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             165:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             166:        // Ditto for our PersistPtr                                                                                                                                             
                             167:        Integer newLocation = oldToNewReferencesLookup.get(Integer.valueOf(persistPointersOffset));                                                                             
                             168:        if(newLocation == null) {                                                                                                                                               
                             169:            throw new HSLFException("Couldn't find the new location of the PersistPtr that used to be at " + persistPointersOffset);                                            
                             170:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             171:        persistPointersOffset = newLocation.intValue();                                                                                                                         
                             172:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             173:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             174:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             175:     * Write the contents of the record back, so it can be written                                                                                                              
                             176:     *  to disk                                                                                                                                                                 
                             177:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             178:    @Override                                                                                                                                                                   
                             179:    public void writeOut(OutputStream out) throws IOException {                                                                                                                 
                             180:        // Header                                                                                                                                                               
                             181:        out.write(_header);                                                                                                                                                     
                             182:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             183:        // Write out the values                                                                                                                                                 
                             184:        writeLittleEndian(lastViewedSlideID,out);                                                                                                                               
                             185:        writeLittleEndian(pptVersion,out);                                                                                                                                      
                             186:        writeLittleEndian(lastUserEditAtomOffset,out);                                                                                                                          
                             187:        writeLittleEndian(persistPointersOffset,out);                                                                                                                           
                             188:        writeLittleEndian(docPersistRef,out);                                                                                                                                   
                             189:        writeLittleEndian(maxPersistWritten,out);                                                                                                                               
                             190:        writeLittleEndian(lastViewType,out);                                                                                                                                    
                             191:        writeLittleEndian(unused,out);                                                                                                                                          
                             192:        if (encryptSessionPersistIdRef != -1) {                                                                                                                                 
                             193:            // optional field                                                                                                                                                   
                             194:            writeLittleEndian(encryptSessionPersistIdRef,out);                                                                                                                  
                             195:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             196:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             197:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             198:    @Override                                                                                                                                                                   
                             199:    public Map<String, Supplier<?>> getGenericProperties() {                                                                                                                    
                             200:        final Map<String, Supplier<?>> m = new LinkedHashMap<>();                                                                                                               
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             poi-scratchpad/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/hslf/record/PersistPtrHolder.java:1-150                                                                                                 
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             1:/* ====================================================================                                                                                                           
                             2:   Licensed to the Apache Software Foundation (ASF) under one or more                                                                                                             
                             3:   contributor license agreements.  See the NOTICE file distributed with                                                                                                          
                             4:   this work for additional information regarding copyright ownership.                                                                                                            
                             5:   The ASF licenses this file to You under the Apache License, Version 2.0                                                                                                        
                             6:   (the "License"); you may not use this file except in compliance with                                                                                                           
                             7:   the License.  You may obtain a copy of the License at                                                                                                                          
                             8:                                                                                                                                                                                  
                             9:       http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0                                                                                                                                 
                             10:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             11:   Unless required by applicable law or agreed to in writing, software                                                                                                           
                             12:   distributed under the License is distributed on an "AS IS" BASIS,                                                                                                             
                             13:   WITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied.                                                                                                      
                             14:   See the License for the specific language governing permissions and                                                                                                           
                             15:   limitations under the License.                                                                                                                                                
                             16:==================================================================== */                                                                                                          
                             17:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             18:package org.apache.poi.hslf.record;                                                                                                                                              
                             19:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             20:import java.io.IOException;                                                                                                                                                      
                             21:import java.io.OutputStream;                                                                                                                                                     
                             22:import java.util.Arrays;                                                                                                                                                         
                             23:import java.util.Collections;                                                                                                                                                    
                             24:import java.util.Comparator;                                                                                                                                                     
                             25:import java.util.HashMap;                                                                                                                                                        
                             26:import java.util.Map;                                                                                                                                                            
                             27:import java.util.Map.Entry;                                                                                                                                                      
                             28:import java.util.function.Supplier;                                                                                                                                              
                             29:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             30:import org.apache.poi.hslf.exceptions.CorruptPowerPointFileException;                                                                                                            
                             31:import org.apache.poi.util.BitField;                                                                                                                                             
                             32:import org.apache.poi.util.BitFieldFactory;                                                                                                                                      
                             33:import org.apache.poi.util.GenericRecordUtil;                                                                                                                                    
                             34:import org.apache.poi.util.IOUtils;                                                                                                                                              
                             35:import org.apache.poi.util.LittleEndian;                                                                                                                                         
                             36:import org.apache.poi.util.LittleEndianConsts;                                                                                                                                   
                             37:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             38:/**                                                                                                                                                                              
                             39: * General holder for PersistPtrFullBlock and PersistPtrIncrementalBlock                                                                                                         
                             40: *  records. We need to handle them specially, since we have to go around                                                                                                        
                             41: *  updating UserEditAtoms if they shuffle about on disk                                                                                                                         
                             42: * These hold references to where slides "live". If the position of a slide                                                                                                      
                             43: *  moves, then we have update all of these. If we come up with a new version                                                                                                    
                             44: *  of a slide, then we have to add one of these to the end of the chain                                                                                                         
                             45: *  (via CurrentUserAtom and UserEditAtom) pointing to the new slide location                                                                                                    
                             46: */                                                                                                                                                                              
                             47:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             48:public final class PersistPtrHolder extends PositionDependentRecordAtom {                                                                                                        
                             49:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             50:    private final byte[] _header;                                                                                                                                                
                             51:    private byte[] _ptrData; // Will need to update this once we allow updates to _slideLocations                                                                                
                             52:    private final long _type;                                                                                                                                                    
                             53:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             54:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             55:     * Holds the lookup for slides to their position on disk.                                                                                                                    
                             56:     * You always need to check the most recent PersistPtrHolder                                                                                                                 
                             57:     *  that knows about a given slide to find the right location                                                                                                                
                             58:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             59:    private final Map<Integer,Integer> _slideLocations;                                                                                                                          
                             60:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             61:    private static final BitField persistIdFld = BitFieldFactory.getInstance(0X000FFFFF);                                                                                        
                             62:    private static final BitField cntPersistFld  = BitFieldFactory.getInstance(0XFFF00000);                                                                                      
                             63:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             64:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             65:     * Return the value we were given at creation, be it 6001 or 6002                                                                                                            
                             66:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             67:    @Override                                                                                                                                                                    
                             68:    public long getRecordType() { return _type; }                                                                                                                                
                             69:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             70:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             71:     * Get the list of slides that this PersistPtrHolder knows about.                                                                                                            
                             72:     * (They will be the keys in the map for looking up the positions                                                                                                            
                             73:     *  of these slides)                                                                                                                                                         
                             74:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             75:    public int[] getKnownSlideIDs() {                                                                                                                                            
                             76:        int[] ids = new int[_slideLocations.size()];                                                                                                                             
                             77:        int i = 0;                                                                                                                                                               
                             78:        for (Integer slideId : _slideLocations.keySet()) {                                                                                                                       
                             79:            ids[i++] = slideId;                                                                                                                                                  
                             80:        }                                                                                                                                                                        
                             81:        return ids;                                                                                                                                                              
                             82:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             83:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             84:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             85:     * Get the lookup from slide numbers to byte offsets, for the slides                                                                                                         
                             86:     *  known about by this PersistPtrHolder.                                                                                                                                    
                             87:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             88:    public Map<Integer,Integer> getSlideLocationsLookup() {                                                                                                                      
                             89:        return Collections.unmodifiableMap(_slideLocations);                                                                                                                     
                             90:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             91:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             92:    /**                                                                                                                                                                          
                             93:     * Create a new holder for a PersistPtr record                                                                                                                               
                             94:     */                                                                                                                                                                          
                             95:    protected PersistPtrHolder(byte[] source, int start, int len) {                                                                                                              
                             96:        // Sanity Checking - including whole header, so treat                                                                                                                    
                             97:        //  length as based of 0, not 8 (including header size based)                                                                                                            
                             98:        if(len < 8) { len = 8; }                                                                                                                                                 
                             99:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             100:        // Treat as an atom, grab and hold everything                                                                                                                           
                             101:        _header = Arrays.copyOfRange(source, start, start+8);                                                                                                                   
                             102:        _type = LittleEndian.getUShort(_header,2);                                                                                                                              
                             103:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             104:        // Try to make sense of the data part:                                                                                                                                  
                             105:        // Data part is made up of a number of these sets:                                                                                                                      
                             106:        //   32 bit info value                                                                                                                                                  
                             107:        //      12 bits count of # of entries                                                                                                                                   
                             108:        //      base number for these entries                                                                                                                                   
                             109:        //   count * 32 bit offsets                                                                                                                                             
                             110:        // Repeat as many times as you have data                                                                                                                                
                             111:        _slideLocations = new HashMap<>();                                                                                                                                      
                             112:        _ptrData = IOUtils.safelyClone(source, start+8, len-8, RecordAtom.getMaxRecordLength());                                                                                
                             113:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             114:        int pos = 0;                                                                                                                                                            
                             115:        while(pos < _ptrData.length) {                                                                                                                                          
                             116:            // Grab the info field                                                                                                                                              
                             117:            int info = LittleEndian.getInt(_ptrData,pos);                                                                                                                       
                             118:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             119:            // First 20 bits = offset number                                                                                                                                    
                             120:            // Remaining 12 bits = offset count                                                                                                                                 
                             121:            int offset_no = persistIdFld.getValue(info);                                                                                                                        
                             122:            int offset_count = cntPersistFld.getValue(info);                                                                                                                    
                             123:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             124:            // Wind on by the 4 byte info header                                                                                                                                
                             125:            pos += 4;                                                                                                                                                           
                             126:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             127:            // Grab the offsets for each of the sheets                                                                                                                          
                             128:            for(int i=0; i<offset_count; i++) {                                                                                                                                 
                             129:                int sheet_no = offset_no + i;                                                                                                                                   
                             130:                int sheet_offset = (int)LittleEndian.getUInt(_ptrData,pos);                                                                                                     
                             131:                _slideLocations.put(sheet_no, sheet_offset);                                                                                                                    
                             132:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             133:                // Wind on by 4 bytes per sheet found                                                                                                                           
                             134:                pos += 4;                                                                                                                                                       
                             135:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             136:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             137:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             138:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             139:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             140:     *  remove all slide references                                                                                                                                             
                             141:     *                                                                                                                                                                          
                             142:     *  Convenience method provided, for easier reviewing of invocations                                                                                                        
                             143:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             144:    public void clear() {                                                                                                                                                       
                             145:        _slideLocations.clear();                                                                                                                                                
                             146:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             147:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             148:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             149:     * Adds a new slide, notes or similar, to be looked up by this.                                                                                                             
                             150:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             poi-scratchpad/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/hslf/record/CurrentUserAtom.java:1-150                                                                                                  
                             ```

                             5:   this work for additional information regarding copyright ownership.                                                                                                            
                             6:   The ASF licenses this file to You under the Apache License, Version 2.0                                                                                                        
                             7:   (the "License"); you may not use this file except in compliance with                                                                                                           
                             8:   the License.  You may obtain a copy of the License at                                                                                                                          
                             9:                                                                                                                                                                                  
                             10:       http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0                                                                                                                                
                             11:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             12:   Unless required by applicable law or agreed to in writing, software                                                                                                           
                             13:   distributed under the License is distributed on an "AS IS" BASIS,                                                                                                             
                             14:   WITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied.                                                                                                      
                             15:   See the License for the specific language governing permissions and                                                                                                           
                             16:   limitations under the License.
