                             59://    Cipher cipher = null;                                                                                                                                                      
                             60:    ChunkedCipherOutputStream cyos;                                                                                                                                              
                             61:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             62:    private static final BitField fieldRecInst = new BitField(0xFFF0);                                                                                                           
                             63:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             64:    private static final int[] BLIB_STORE_ENTRY_PARTS = {                                                                                                                        
                             65:            1,     // btWin32                                                                                                                                                    
                             66:            1,     // btMacOS                                                                                                                                                    
                             67:            16,    // rgbUid                                                                                                                                                     
                             68:            2,     // tag                                                                                                                                                        
                             69:            4,     // size                                                                                                                                                       
                             70:            4,     // cRef                                                                                                                                                       
                             71:            4,     // foDelay                                                                                                                                                    
                             72:            1,     // unused1                                                                                                                                                    
                             73:            1,     // cbName (@ index 33)                                                                                                                                        
                             74:            1,     // unused2                                                                                                                                                    
                             75:            1,     // unused3                                                                                                                                                    
                             76:    };                                                                                                                                                                           
                             77:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             78:    protected HSLFSlideShowEncrypted(DocumentEncryptionAtom dea) {                                                                                                               
                             79:        this.dea = dea;                                                                                                                                                          
                             80:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             81:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             82:    protected HSLFSlideShowEncrypted(byte[] docstream, NavigableMap<Integer,Record> recordMap) {                                                                                 
                             83:        // check for DocumentEncryptionAtom, which would be at the last offset                                                                                                   
                             84:        // need to ignore already set UserEdit and PersistAtoms                                                                                                                  
                             85:        UserEditAtom userEditAtomWithEncryption = null;                                                                                                                          
                             86:        for (Map.Entry<Integer, Record> me : recordMap.descendingMap().entrySet()) {                                                                                             
                             87:            org.apache.poi.hslf.record.Record r = me.getValue();                                                                                                                 
                             88:            if (!(r instanceof UserEditAtom)) {                                                                                                                                  
                             89:                continue;                                                                                                                                                        
                             90:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             91:            UserEditAtom uea = (UserEditAtom)r;                                                                                                                                  
                             92:            if (uea.getEncryptSessionPersistIdRef() != -1) {                                                                                                                     
                             93:                userEditAtomWithEncryption = uea;                                                                                                                                
                             94:                break;                                                                                                                                                           
                             95:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             96:        }                                                                                                                                                                        
                             97:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             98:        if (userEditAtomWithEncryption == null) {                                                                                                                                
                             99:            dea = null;                                                                                                                                                          
                             100:            return;                                                                                                                                                             
                             101:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             102:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             103:        org.apache.poi.hslf.record.Record r = recordMap.get(userEditAtomWithEncryption.getPersistPointersOffset());                                                             
                             104:        if (!(r instanceof PersistPtrHolder)) {                                                                                                                                 
                             105:            throw new RecordFormatException("Encountered an unexpected record-type: " + r);                                                                                     
                             106:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             107:        PersistPtrHolder ptr = (PersistPtrHolder)r;                                                                                                                             
                             108:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             109:        Integer encOffset = ptr.getSlideLocationsLookup().get(userEditAtomWithEncryption.getEncryptSessionPersistIdRef());                                                      
                             110:        if (encOffset == null) {                                                                                                                                                
                             111:            // encryption info doesn't exist anymore                                                                                                                            
                             112:            // SoftMaker Freeoffice produces such invalid files - check for "SMNativeObjData" ole stream                                                                        
                             113:            dea = null;                                                                                                                                                         
                             114:            return;                                                                                                                                                             
                             115:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             116:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             117:        r = recordMap.get(encOffset);                                                                                                                                           
                             118:        if (r == null) {                                                                                                                                                        
                             119:            r = Record.buildRecordAtOffset(docstream, encOffset);                                                                                                               
                             120:            recordMap.put(encOffset, r);                                                                                                                                        
                             121:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             122:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             123:        if (!(r instanceof DocumentEncryptionAtom)) {                                                                                                                           
                             124:            throw new EncryptedPowerPointFileException("Did not have a DocumentEncryptionAtom: " + r);                                                                          
                             125:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             126:        this.dea = (DocumentEncryptionAtom)r;                                                                                                                                   
                             127:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             128:        String pass = Biff8EncryptionKey.getCurrentUserPassword();                                                                                                              
                             129:        EncryptionInfo ei = getEncryptionInfo();                                                                                                                                
                             130:        try {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             131:            if (ei == null || ei.getDecryptor() == null) {                                                                                                                      
                             132:                throw new IllegalStateException("Invalid encryption-info: " + ei);                                                                                              
                             133:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             134:            if(!ei.getDecryptor().verifyPassword(pass != null ? pass : Decryptor.DEFAULT_PASSWORD)) {                                                                           
                             135:                throw new EncryptedPowerPointFileException("PowerPoint file is encrypted. The correct password needs to be set via                                              
                             Biff8EncryptionKey.setCurrentUserPassword()");                                                                                                                                      
                             136:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             137:        } catch (GeneralSecurityException e) {                                                                                                                                  
                             138:            throw new EncryptedPowerPointFileException(e);                                                                                                                      
                             139:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             140:     }                                                                                                                                                                          
                             141:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             142:    public DocumentEncryptionAtom getDocumentEncryptionAtom() {                                                                                                                 
                             143:        return dea;                                                                                                                                                             
                             144:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             145:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             146:    protected EncryptionInfo getEncryptionInfo() {                                                                                                                              
                             147:        return (dea != null) ? dea.getEncryptionInfo() : null;                                                                                                                  
                             148:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             149:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             150:    protected OutputStream encryptRecord(OutputStream plainStream, int persistId, org.apache.poi.hslf.record.Record record) {                                                   
                             151:        boolean isPlain = (dea == null                                                                                                                                          
                             152:            || record instanceof UserEditAtom                                                                                                                                   
                             153:            || record instanceof PersistPtrHolder                                                                                                                               
                             154:            || record instanceof DocumentEncryptionAtom                                                                                                                         
                             155:        );                                                                                                                                                                      
                             156:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             157:        try {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             158:            if (isPlain) {                                                                                                                                                      
                             159:                if (cyos != null) {                                                                                                                                             
                             160:                    // write cached data to stream                                                                                                                              
                             161:                    cyos.flush();                                                                                                                                               
                             162:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             163:                return plainStream;                                                                                                                                             
                             164:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             165:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             166:            if (cyos == null) {                                                                                                                                                 
                             167:                Encryptor enc = getEncryptionInfo().getEncryptor();                                                                                                             
                             168:                enc.setChunkSize(-1);                                                                                                                                           
                             169:                cyos = enc.getDataStream(plainStream, 0);                                                                                                                       
                             170:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             171:            cyos.initCipherForBlock(persistId, false);                                                                                                                          
                             172:        } catch (Exception e) {                                                                                                                                                 
                             173:            throw new EncryptedPowerPointFileException(e);                                                                                                                      
                             174:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             175:        return cyos;                                                                                                                                                            
                             176:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             177:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             178:    private static void readFully(ChunkedCipherInputStream ccis, byte[] docstream, int offset, int len) throws IOException {                                                    
                             179:        if (IOUtils.readFully(ccis, docstream, offset, len) == -1) {                                                                                                            
                             180:            throw new EncryptedPowerPointFileException("unexpected EOF");                                                                                                       
                             181:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             182:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             183:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             184:    protected void decryptRecord(byte[] docstream, int persistId, int offset) {                                                                                                 
                             185:        if (dea == null) {                                                                                                                                                      
                             186:            return;                                                                                                                                                             
                             187:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             188:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             189:        Decryptor dec = getEncryptionInfo().getDecryptor();                                                                                                                     
                             190:        dec.setChunkSize(-1);                                                                                                                                                   
                             191:        try (LittleEndianByteArrayInputStream lei = new LittleEndianByteArrayInputStream(docstream, offset);                                                                    
                             192:                ChunkedCipherInputStream ccis = (ChunkedCipherInputStream)dec.getDataStream(lei, docstream.length-offset, 0)) {                                                 
                             193:            ccis.initCipherForBlock(persistId);                                                                                                                                 
                             194:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             195:            // decrypt header and read length to be decrypted                                                                                                                   
                             196:            readFully(ccis, docstream, offset, 8);                                                                                                                              
                             197:            // decrypt the rest of the record                                                                                                                                   
                             198:            int rlen = (int)LittleEndian.getUInt(docstream, offset+4);                                                                                                          
                             199:            readFully(ccis, docstream, offset+8, rlen);                                                                                                                         
                             200:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             poi-scratchpad/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/hslf/usermodel/HSLFSlideShowImpl.java:365-500                                                                                           
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             365:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             366:    public DocumentEncryptionAtom getDocumentEncryptionAtom() {                                                                                                                 
                             367:        for (Record r : _records) {                                                                                                                                             
                             368:            if (r instanceof DocumentEncryptionAtom) {                                                                                                                          
                             369:                return (DocumentEncryptionAtom) r;                                                                                                                              
                             370:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             371:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             372:        return null;                                                                                                                                                            
                             373:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             374:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             375:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             376:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             377:     * Find the "Current User" stream, and load it                                                                                                                              
                             378:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             379:    private void readCurrentUserStream() {                                                                                                                                      
                             380:        try {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             381:            currentUser = new CurrentUserAtom(getDirectory());                                                                                                                  
                             382:        } catch (IOException ie) {                                                                                                                                              
                             383:            LOG.atError().withThrowable(ie).log("Error finding Current User Atom");                                                                                             
                             384:            currentUser = new CurrentUserAtom();                                                                                                                                
                             385:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             386:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             387:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             388:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             389:     * Find any other streams from the filesystem, and load them                                                                                                                
                             390:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             391:    private void readOtherStreams() {                                                                                                                                           
                             392:        // Currently, there aren't any                                                                                                                                          
                             393:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             394:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             395:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             396:     * Find and read in pictures contained in this presentation.                                                                                                                
                             397:     * This is lazily called as and when we want to touch pictures.                                                                                                             
                             398:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             399:    private void readPictures() throws IOException {                                                                                                                            
                             400:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             401:        // if the presentation doesn't contain pictures, will use an empty collection instead                                                                                   
                             402:        if (!getDirectory().hasEntryCaseInsensitive("Pictures")) {                                                                                                              
                             403:            _pictures = new ArrayList<>();                                                                                                                                      
                             404:            return;                                                                                                                                                             
                             405:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             406:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             407:        final Entry en = getDirectory().getEntryCaseInsensitive("Pictures");                                                                                                    
                             408:        if (!(en instanceof DocumentEntry)) {                                                                                                                                   
                             409:            throw new IllegalArgumentException("Had unexpected type of entry for name: Pictures: " + en.getClass());                                                            
                             410:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             411:        DocumentEntry entry = (DocumentEntry) en;                                                                                                                               
                             412:        EscherContainerRecord blipStore = getBlipStore();                                                                                                                       
                             413:        byte[] pictstream;                                                                                                                                                      
                             414:        try (DocumentInputStream is = getDirectory().createDocumentInputStream(entry)) {                                                                                        
                             415:            pictstream = IOUtils.toByteArray(is, entry.getSize(), MAX_IMAGE_LENGTH);                                                                                            
                             416:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             417:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             418:        List<PictureFactory> factories = new ArrayList<>();                                                                                                                     
                             419:        try (HSLFSlideShowEncrypted decryptData = new HSLFSlideShowEncrypted(getDocumentEncryptionAtom())) {                                                                    
                             420:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             421:            int pos = 0;                                                                                                                                                        
                             422:            // An empty picture record (length 0) will take up 8 bytes                                                                                                          
                             423:            while (pos <= (pictstream.length - HSLFPictureData.PREAMBLE_SIZE)) {                                                                                                
                             424:                int offset = pos;                                                                                                                                               
                             425:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             426:                decryptData.decryptPicture(pictstream, offset);                                                                                                                 
                             427:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             428:                // Image signature                                                                                                                                              
                             429:                int signature = LittleEndian.getUShort(pictstream, pos);                                                                                                        
                             430:                pos += LittleEndianConsts.SHORT_SIZE;                                                                                                                           
                             431:                // Image type + 0xF018                                                                                                                                          
                             432:                int type = LittleEndian.getUShort(pictstream, pos);                                                                                                             
                             433:                pos += LittleEndianConsts.SHORT_SIZE;                                                                                                                           
                             434:                // Image size (excluding the 8 byte header)                                                                                                                     
                             435:                int imgsize = LittleEndian.getInt(pictstream, pos);                                                                                                             
                             436:                pos += LittleEndianConsts.INT_SIZE;                                                                                                                             
                             437:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             438:                // When parsing the BStoreDelay stream, [MS-ODRAW] says that we                                                                                                 
                             439:                //  should terminate if the type isn't 0xf007 or 0xf018->0xf117                                                                                                 
                             440:                if (!((type == 0xf007) || (type >= 0xf018 && type <= 0xf117))) {                                                                                                
                             441:                    break;                                                                                                                                                      
                             442:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             443:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             444:                // The image size must be 0 or greater                                                                                                                          
                             445:                // (0 is allowed, but odd, since we do wind on by the header each                                                                                               
                             446:                //  time, so we won't get stuck)                                                                                                                                
                             447:                if (imgsize < 0) {                                                                                                                                              
                             448:                    throw new CorruptPowerPointFileException("The file contains a picture, at position " + factories.size() + ", which has a negatively sized                   
                             data length, so we can't trust any of the picture data");                                                                                                                           
                             449:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             450:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             451:                // If the type (including the bonus 0xF018) is 0, skip it                                                                                                       
                             452:                PictureType pt = PictureType.forNativeID(type - 0xF018);                                                                                                        
                             453:                if (pt == null) {                                                                                                                                               
                             454:                    LOG.atError().log("Problem reading picture: Invalid image type 0, on picture with length {}.\nYour document will probably become corrupted                  
                             if you save it! Position: {}", box(imgsize),box(pos));                                                                                                                              
                             455:                } else {                                                                                                                                                        
                             456:                    //The pictstream can be truncated halfway through a picture.                                                                                                
                             457:                    //This is not a problem if the pictstream contains extra pictures                                                                                           
                             458:                    //that are not used in any slide -- BUG-60305                                                                                                               
                             459:                    if (pos + imgsize > pictstream.length) {                                                                                                                    
                             460:                        LOG.atWarn().log("\"Pictures\" stream may have ended early. In some circumstances, this is not a problem; " +                                           
                             461:                                "in others, this could indicate a corrupt file");                                                                                               
                             462:                        break;                                                                                                                                                  
                             463:                    }                                                                                                                                                           
                             464:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             465:                    // Copy the data, ready to pass to PictureData                                                                                                              
                             466:                    byte[] imgdata = IOUtils.safelyClone(pictstream, pos, imgsize, MAX_RECORD_LENGTH);                                                                          
                             467:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             468:                    factories.add(new PictureFactory(blipStore, pt, imgdata, offset, signature));                                                                               
                             469:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             470:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             471:                pos += imgsize;                                                                                                                                                 
                             472:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             473:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             474:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             475:        matchPicturesAndRecords(factories, blipStore);                                                                                                                          
                             476:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             477:        List<HSLFPictureData> pictures = new ArrayList<>();                                                                                                                     
                             478:        for (PictureFactory it : factories)      {                                                                                                                              
                             479:            try {                                                                                                                                                               
                             480:                HSLFPictureData pict = it.build();                                                                                                                              
                             481:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             482:                pict.setIndex(pictures.size() + 1);        // index is 1-based                                                                                                  
                             483:                pictures.add(pict);                                                                                                                                             
                             484:            } catch (IllegalArgumentException e) {                                                                                                                              
                             485:                LOG.atError().withThrowable(e).log("Problem reading picture. Your document will probably become corrupted if you save it!");                                    
                             486:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             487:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             488:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             489:        _pictures = pictures;                                                                                                                                                   
                             490:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             491:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             492:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             493:     * Matches all of the {@link PictureFactory PictureFactories} for a slideshow with {@link EscherBSERecord}s in the                                                          
                             494:     * Blip Store for the slideshow.                                                                                                                                            
                             495:     * <p>                                                                                                                                                                      
                             496:     * When reading a slideshow into memory, we have to match the records in the Blip Store with the factories                                                                  
                             497:     * representing picture in the pictures stream. This can be difficult, as presentations might have incorrectly                                                              
                             498:     * formatted data. This function attempts to perform matching using multiple heuristics to increase the likelihood                                                          
                             499:     * of finding all pairs, while aiming to reduce the likelihood of associating incorrect pairs.                                                                              
                             500:     *                                                                                                                                                                          
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             poi-scratchpad/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/hslf/usermodel/HSLFSlideShowImpl.java:172-250                                                                                           
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             172:    public HSLFSlideShowImpl(DirectoryNode dir) throws IOException {                                                                                                            
                             173:        super(handleDualStorage(dir));                                                                                                                                          
                             174:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             175:        try {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             176:            // First up, grab the "Current User" stream                                                                                                                         
                             177:            // We need this before we can detect Encrypted Documents                                                                                                            
                             178:            readCurrentUserStream();                                                                                                                                            
                             179:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             180:            // Next up, grab the data that makes up the                                                                                                                         
                             181:            //  PowerPoint stream                                                                                                                                               
                             182:            readPowerPointStream();                                                                                                                                             
                             183:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             184:            // Now, build records based on the PowerPoint stream                                                                                                                
                             185:            buildRecords();                                                                                                                                                     
                             186:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             187:            // Look for any other streams                                                                                                                                       
                             188:            readOtherStreams();                                                                                                                                                 
                             189:        } catch (RuntimeException | IOException e) {                                                                                                                            
                             190:            // clean up the filesystem when we cannot read it here to avoid                                                                                                     
                             191:            // leaking file handles                                                                                                                                             
                             192:            dir.getFileSystem().close();                                                                                                                                        
                             193:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             194:            throw e;                                                                                                                                                            
                             195:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             196:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             197:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             198:    private static DirectoryNode handleDualStorage(DirectoryNode dir) throws IOException {                                                                                      
                             199:        // when there's a dual storage entry, use it, as the outer document can't be read quite probably ...                                                                    
                             200:        if (!dir.hasEntryCaseInsensitive(PP97_DOCUMENT)) {                                                                                                                      
                             201:            return dir;                                                                                                                                                         
                             202:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             203:        return (DirectoryNode) dir.getEntryCaseInsensitive(PP97_DOCUMENT);                                                                                                      
                             204:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             205:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             206:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             207:     * Constructs a new, empty, Powerpoint document.                                                                                                                            
                             208:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             209:    public static HSLFSlideShowImpl create() {                                                                                                                                  
                             210:        try (InputStream is = HSLFSlideShowImpl.class.getResourceAsStream("/org/apache/poi/hslf/data/empty.ppt")) {                                                             
                             211:            if (is == null) {                                                                                                                                                   
                             212:                throw new HSLFException("Missing resource 'empty.ppt'");                                                                                                        
                             213:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             214:            return new HSLFSlideShowImpl(is);                                                                                                                                   
                             215:        } catch (IOException e) {                                                                                                                                               
                             216:            throw new HSLFException(e);                                                                                                                                         
                             217:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             218:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             219:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             220:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             221:     * Extracts the main PowerPoint document stream from the                                                                                                                    
                             222:     * POI file, ready to be passed                                                                                                                                             
                             223:     *                                                                                                                                                                          
                             224:     * @throws IOException when the powerpoint can't be read                                                                                                                    
                             225:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             226:    private void readPowerPointStream() throws IOException {                                                                                                                    
                             227:        final DirectoryNode dir = getDirectory();                                                                                                                               
                             228:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             229:        if (!dir.hasEntryCaseInsensitive(POWERPOINT_DOCUMENT) && dir.hasEntryCaseInsensitive(PP95_DOCUMENT)) {                                                                  
                             230:            throw new OldPowerPointFormatException("You seem to have supplied a PowerPoint95 file, which isn't supported");                                                     
                             231:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             232:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             233:        // Get the main document stream                                                                                                                                         
                             234:        final Entry entry = dir.getEntryCaseInsensitive(POWERPOINT_DOCUMENT);                                                                                                   
                             235:        if (!(entry instanceof DocumentEntry)) {                                                                                                                                
                             236:            throw new IllegalArgumentException("Had unexpected type of entry for name: " + POWERPOINT_DOCUMENT + ": " + entry.getClass());                                      
                             237:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             238:        DocumentEntry docProps = (DocumentEntry) entry;                                                                                                                         
                             239:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             240:        // Grab the document stream                                                                                                                                             
                             241:        int len = docProps.getSize();                                                                                                                                           
                             242:        try (InputStream is = dir.createDocumentInputStream(docProps)) {                                                                                                        
                             243:            _docstream = IOUtils.toByteArray(is, len, MAX_DOCUMENT_SIZE);                                                                                                       
                             244:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             245:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             246:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             247:    /**                                                                                                                                                                         
                             248:     * Builds the list of records, based on the contents                                                                                                                        
                             249:     * of the PowerPoint stream                                                                                                                                                 
                             250:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             poi-scratchpad/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/hslf/usermodel/HSLFSlideShowImpl.java:500-620                                                                                           
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             500:     *                                                                                                                                                                          
                             501:     * @param factories Factories for creating {@link HSLFPictureData} out of the pictures stream.                                                                              
                             502:     * @param blipStore Blip Store of the presentation being loaded.                                                                                                            
                             503:     */                                                                                                                                                                         
                             504:    private static void matchPicturesAndRecords(List<PictureFactory> factories, EscherContainerRecord blipStore) {
